{"name":"均衡 Balance","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"gm-notes":{"notes":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>每天日出時刻，骰一個1d6。</p>\n<p>1 - 接下來的一天，你的抉擇將被<strong>邪惡的意志</strong>所掌握。</p>\n<p>2~5 - 今天你的意志依然在兩者中徘徊。</p>\n<p>6 - 接下來的一天，你的抉擇將被<strong>善良的意志</strong>所引導。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>這張卡片的效應可以被@Item[seOAvDIoyf2Sa0SR]{高等復原術}移除。</p>"},"cf":{"id":"temp_mxco2n8eclo","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Many Things","color":"#6b5988"}},"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>兩種意志存在你體內，一則以善一則以惡。</p>\n<p>其真實樣貌揭曉於曙光。</p>","img":"modules/SupersHomebrewPack/icons/deck_of_many_things/balance.png","_id":"WJy2risehxTTHF6g"}
