{"name":"玩家筆記_凡戴爾","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_yopfjqluiwb","path":"過去的紀錄#/CF_SEP/凡戴爾的失落礦坑","color":"#f0a524"}},"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">木匠提爾被紅標幫殺害，妻小被俘虜。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">提爾的家人：米爾納 丹卓（妻子），納斯 age 13(弟弟)、奈沙 age 18(姊姊)。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">玻璃手杖：在做著奇怪的藥水、經常待在在莊園西邊的房間。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">石丘旅店老闆娘：崔琳娜石丘</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">伊阿諾 阿布雷克，30多歲，蓄黑鬍的人類法師（修達的朋友）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">甘達倫：把甘德倫帶去黑蜘蛛那裡</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">修達：深水城的領主聯盟鐵騎隊成員（徽章是獅鷲）</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">修女（豎琴手同盟）：尋找阿加莎女妖，他知道博哲托爾的魔法書在哪</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">阿加莎女妖住在兔莓</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">達朗 埃德瑪（巨龍海岸指揮官）：東北方的古蕭井有很多不死生物，那裏曾經是古老帝國奈瑟瑞爾的瞭望塔，可能有危險的魔法。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">鎮長：哈賓威斯特</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">鎮長：100 GP for 獸人的耳朵&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">凡德霖礦工兌換所：打倒玻璃手帳、取回信件領賞100ＧＰ</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">甘德倫被送到 克拉摩城堡</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">甘德倫希望重新開始潮音礦坑的開採</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">鍍銀劍鞘長劍（上頭畫著展翅狩獵的鳥）：稱號「黑影」的騎士 奧爾迪斯 崔森德的配件</p>","_id":"iiZSi8ygonPlCBLk"}
