{"_id":"jeVFK26R9hFnIbGP","name":"神秘遺跡牆上的碑文","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"folder":"","flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_c9bgnfgyru","path":"萊安娜與羅曼的大冒險","color":"#de9f17"},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.lzjMeSrkaPqynTMe"}},"content":"<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color: #191813;\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">LuBa</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color: #191813;\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">The spells on these locks are all the same.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Though each possesses a unique name.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Count on your answer to unlock the way.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">But use the wrong key to your dismay.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>"}
{"name":"NPC GM Note","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"gm-notes":{"notes":"<p>遭遇:</p>\n<p>1</p>\n<p>@Actor[WFdbTxvaSQinjrYU]{枯針怪 Needle Blight}X2</p>\n<p>@Actor[SGeh6l5DFrzSvopA]{枯藤怪 Vine Blight}X1</p>\n<hr />\n<p>2</p>"},"cf":{"id":"temp_c9bgnfgyru","path":"萊安娜與羅曼的大冒險","color":"#de9f17"}},"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>瓦喬爾 312歲 費爾柏格 藥草師/3等德魯伊 ；</p>\n<p>沉默寡言，住在潛行森林邊緣，身高8.3呎(2.5m)，身邊有一隻叫做嫩芽的雄鹿陪伴。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大哥布林</p>\n<p>柯基(Corg)</p>\n<p>索格(Sog)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>哥布林</p>\n<p>德魯普(Droop)</p>\n<p>鼻涕(Snot)</p>\n<p>鼻屎(Booger)</p>\n<p>蛙臉(Frogface)</p>","_id":"Ll510wDCGttW8gDr"}
{"_id":"o5bz7uPHU1d4qPrF","name":"神祕遺跡 GM Note","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"folder":"","flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_c9bgnfgyru","path":"萊安娜與羅曼的大冒險","color":"#de9f17"}},"content":"<p>這個房間的是500年前惡名昭彰的斑貓人法師盧巴(Luba)的創造物，她最著名的法術便是將生物給困在圖畫之中；</p>\n<p>謠傳她在生前打造了4把特殊的鑰匙，只要將集齊4把鑰匙就能找到盧巴最珍貴的寶物。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>盔甲走廊:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>有兩隻守衛之手漂浮其中，想要通過需要禮貌地與它握手；若是攻擊/推開它們，守衛之手便會反擊造成4d10鈍擊傷害。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>一踏入房間，空中便會浮現出一句話(通用語)；Foes don't proceed, only friends shall we be.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>隱藏門:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>在那被哥布林們佔據的房間中，有個隱藏起來的門；</p>\n<p>在那牆壁的上方用精靈語寫著:</p>\n<p>What has 4 letters, sometimes has 9, but never has 5?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>解答: Yes /沒錯/是的；當回答出這些答案，牆壁就會自行滑開，露出後面的房間。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>最後的房間中:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>在中央的牆壁上，用著龍語刻著大大的LuBa；在那之下寫著以下的文字:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The spells on these locks are all the same.</p>\n<p>Though each possesses a unique name.</p>\n<p>Count on your answer to unlock the way.</p>\n<p>But use the wrong key to your dismay.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>牆上的圖畫由上至下；</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>巨型蝙蝠 Giant Bat(3)</p>\n<p>@Actor[y4nqfdY4NHWPntrK]{Giant Bat 巨蝙蝠}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>巨型狼蛛 Giant Wolf Spider(6)</p>\n<p>@Actor[PgTxkyfkzTqEHV1c]{Giant Wolf Spider 巨型狼蛛}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>巨型毒蛇 Giant Poisonous Snake(5)</p>\n<p>@Actor[zbcVJv5dpeiGyq84]{Giant Poisonous Snake 巨毒蛇}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>野狼 Wolf(4)</p>\n<p>@Actor[EZv1gG154BOx3sR2]{Wolf 狼}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>當在石台上放置錯誤的鑰匙就會在房間左方的兩個召喚陣中召喚相應的野獸朝房內的所有生物攻擊；</p>\n<p>召喚出的野獸會存在8小時才會消失。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>當成功插入4把鑰匙時，房間中央的傳送法陣便會開啟；進入的角色會被傳送至位面的隙縫間，一個由盧巴創造出來的小房間，裡面放著...。</p>"}
